text: Romana Trajkovska (; born 6 May 1993) is a Swiss–Macedonian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Nationalliga A club FC Rapperswil-Jona and the North Macedonia women's national team. She has been a member of the Switzerland women's national under-19 team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Macedonian women's footballers Category:North Macedonia women's international footballers Category:Swiss women's footballers Category:Swiss people of Macedonian descent Category:Nationalliga A (women's football) players Category:FC Rapperswil-Jona players
